name: CNTK version 2.2 (Windows+Linux)
body:
This release of the Microsoft Cognitive Toolkit (CNTK) supports both **Windows** and **Linux** on **64bit** platforms.

This release contains versions for both **GPU** and **CPU-only** systems.

This release also contains GPU versions supporting [1bit-SGD](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cognitive-toolkit/Enabling-1bit-SGD). **Please note that ALL binaries in the version supporting 1bit-SGD are licensed under specific [1bit-SGD License](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cognitive-toolkit/CNTK-1bit-SGD-License) which is MORE restrictive, than the major CNTK License.**

See [Release Notes](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cognitive-toolkit/ReleaseNotes/CNTK_2_2_Release_Notes) or download them as a separate file using the link below.

To set up this release on your system, please read the Install instructions in the root of the correspondent archive and [Binary Setup instructions in CNTK Wiki](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cognitive-toolkit/Setup-CNTK-on-your-machine).

### Windows

---
- [CNTK for Windows v.2.2 CPU only](https://cntk.ai/dlwc-2.2.html)
- [CNTK for Windows v.2.2 GPU](https://cntk.ai/dlwg-2.2.html)
- [CNTK for Windows v.2.2 GPU with 1bit-SGD](https://cntk.ai/dlw1-2.2.html)
- NuGet Packages:
  - [CNTK, CPU-Only Build](https://www.nuget.org/packages/CNTK.CPUOnly/2.2.0)
  - [CNTK, GPU Build](https://www.nuget.org/packages/CNTK.GPU/2.2.0)
  - [CNTK, UWP CPU-Only Build](http://www.nuget.org/packages/CNTK.UWP.CPUOnly/2.2.0)
  - [CNTK CPU-only Model Evaluation Libraries (MKL based)](http://www.nuget.org/packages/Microsoft.Research.CNTK.CpuEval-mkl/2.2.0)
    Package description and instructions are [here](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cognitive-toolkit/NuGet-Package).

### Linux

---
- [CNTK for Linux v.2.2 CPU only](https://cntk.ai/dllc-2.2.html)
- [CNTK for Linux v.2.2 GPU](https://cntk.ai/dllg-2.2.html)
- [CNTK for Linux v.2.2 GPU with 1bit-SGD](https://cntk.ai/dll1-2.2.html)
- [Images at Docker Hub](https://hub.docker.com/r/microsoft/cntk/)

name: CNTK version 1.1 (Windows+Linux)
body:
This release of Computational Network Toolkit (CNTK) supports both **Windows** and **Linux** on **64bit** platforms.

This release contains versions for both **GPU** and **CPU-only** systems.

This release also contains GPU versions supporting [1bit-SGD](../../wiki/Enabling-1bit-SGD). **Please note that ALL binaries in the version supporting 1bit-SGD are licensed under specific [1bit-SGD License](https://cntk1bitsgd.codeplex.com/license) which is MORE restrictive, than the major CNTK License. This is especially important if you plan to use CNTK in Production of Commercial environments.** 

To set up this release on your system, please read the Install instructions in the root of the correspondent archive and [Binary Setup instructions in CNTK Wiki](../../wiki/CNTK-Binary-Download-and-Configuration).

### Windows

- [CNTK for Windows v.1.1 CPU only](http://cntk.ai/dlwc.html)
- [CNTK for Windows v.1.1 GPU](http://cntk.ai/dlwg.html)

- [CNTK for Linux v.1.1 GPU](http://cntk.ai/dllg.html)
- [CNTK for Linux v.1.1 GPU with 1bit-SGD](http://cntk.ai/dll1.html)
